{"tid":1135290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦施壓「逐步收入鳥籠」","createTime":"2019-05-02T08:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T09:12:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5253ee0bee702767d2a1fc1dc6723798d04864a3","tid":1135290,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:15:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190502/20668909\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190502%2F20668909&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=0565fb92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190502%2F20668909&h=5af80ed3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190502/20668909</a><br />\n<br />\n中聯辦施壓「逐步收入鳥籠」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190502/large/16436407.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190502%2Flarge%2F16436407.jpg&h=5c4a8286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n五四升旗禮由香港各界青少年活動委員會主辦，包含青少年制服團體步操環節。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「佢點樣去包裝件事，我哋都聞得到嗰種味道」。加入制服團體逾20年的陳先生（化名）不滿受壓轉用中式步操，他說：「你想我哋本身精髓慢慢咁樣變（中式步操），一年變、兩年變、三年就變成一個習慣。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：五四百周年升旗禮 解放軍施特訓七制服團體擬轉中式步操<br />\n<br />\n主辦單位承認安排訓練<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員劉銳紹認為，去年中聯辦青年工作部部長陳林約見制服團體，已有壓力轉用中式步操，「一個好大意識形態網籠罩住成個香港，有意無意間透露出嚟壓力。呢啲所謂選擇已經係逐步逐步被收入鳥籠」。<br />\n<br />\n童軍總會回覆《蘋果》指，派員出席解放軍中式步操訓練，旨在觀摩及學習相關知識，童軍總會在五四升旗禮將採用傳統步操。香港少年領袖團則指，曾派出兩名團員出席解放軍中式步操訓練，有關團員亦會嘗試訓練其他參與五四升旗禮的團員，但最終會否在升旗禮中使用中式步操，需視乎團員能否掌握中式步操技巧。香港航空青年團則指，該團對任何訓練、交流和活動均持開放態度。<br />\n<br />\n主辦五四升旗禮的香港各界青少年活動委員會回覆《蘋果》指，各隊制服團體的決定不會影響他們參加升旗禮活動任何環節，而各隊制服團體也毋須在活動前通報所採用的步操方式。至於解放軍中式步操訓練，委員會指與解放軍聯絡，安排參觀營地及學習中式步操。<br />\n<br />\n■記者潘柏林、周詠雯  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n五四百周年升旗禮解放軍施特訓 七制服團體擬轉中式步操<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n撞死小黃牛 的士不顧而<br />\n<br />\n五四百周年升旗禮 解放軍施特訓七制服團體擬轉中式步操"},{"pid":"e5eebf48cd9d9c0513caf3addbfb60bba678c54c","tid":1135290,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20100525/photo/0525-00174-001b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20100525%2Fphoto%2F0525-00174-001b1.jpg&h=17f80c09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n收入鳥籠"},{"pid":"9cffe5db45f493a19f3f7234db72779328d4086c","tid":1135290,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20180321/s00007/adbf916ec2b2b5ff79a165ed89dd85de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20180321%2Fs00007%2Fadbf916ec2b2b5ff79a165ed89dd85de.jpg&h=ce85624e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"031ac0ee2269785e4888ed44b85fe9318147e22c","tid":1135290,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180322/_2018032206195926787.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180322%2F_2018032206195926787.jpg&h=4cca5a93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c55522a69597e063f9e7a41fe7c7d1e0088ef85","tid":1135290,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://mk0masterinsighayvuk.kinstacdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/carriehelena.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmk0masterinsighayvuk.kinstacdn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2Fcarriehelena.jpg&h=c7491ece&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"421b143ec1481dbcf2725cc0d8f787e95dee7d18","tid":1135290,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e5eebf48cd9d9c0513caf3addbfb60bba678c54c","tid":1135290,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"